		Scenario-specific underlay rules. 
			
		name - the VASL SSR name
			
		image - the image name
			
		color - the VASL color name
			
			
		Example:
			
			<underlaySSRule name="WallToCactus" image="CactusPattern.gif">
				
				<color name="WallBrown" />
				
